@startuml
title Exception Flow: Comment Submission Fails

actor User
participant WebInterface
participant CommentControl
database Database

User -> WebInterface: submitComment(postID, text)
activate WebInterface
WebInterface -> CommentControl: createComment(postID, userID, text)
activate CommentControl
CommentControl -> Database: insertComment(...)
activate Database
Database --> CommentControl: error(DatabaseConnectionError)
deactivate Database
CommentControl --> WebInterface: returnError("Comment submission failed")
deactivate CommentControl
WebInterface --> User: displayErrorMessage("Unable to post comment. Please try again.")
deactivate WebInterface

note over Database, CommentControl
System detects failure and returns immediately.
end note

@enduml
